Dartmouth-Hitchcock Medical Center

                    Dartmouth-Hitchcock Medical Center operates a general medical hospital. It is a nonprofit academic health system. The firm health care professionals offers clinical services, education, research, nursing, specialty referrals, and resources. The company was founded in 1893 and is headquartered in Lebanon, NH.                  




